    <div class="documentTop">
      <h1>Press centre</h1>
      
      <p>The Press and Communications Division deals with press enquiries to the Ministry’s political leadership and the Ministry. </p>
<p><strong>Press phone<br /></strong>+47 22 24 83 84 (day time) <br />+47 916 73 519 (evenings and weekends)</p>
<p>Inquiries outside of these times should be directed to the communications manager. Media inquiries may also be sent to <img id='Eoi_1' class='obfimg' src='/images/emailimages/5f5f66fad0222198403c0e7e11422f20.png' alt='' /><script type="text/javascript"><!--
document.write(dc('Eoi_1', 'A896C98794C7C686D8CDCC86CCC9E8CDDBDBCDDAD8968AC7C686D8CDCC86CCC9E8CDDBDBCDDAD892C7DCC4C1C9C58A95CECDDAC088C994'));//--></script>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;<br />News subscription<br /></strong>You can subscribe to news from the Ministry on RSS.&nbsp;<br />•&nbsp;<a href="/en/dep/aid/whats-new/rss.html?id=478818">RSS feed</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can also recieve news and press releases on your e-mail. This service is only provided in Norwegian.&nbsp;<br />•&nbsp;<a href="/nb/dep/ad/pressesenter/abonner.html?id=450417">News subscription (Norwegian)</a></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;<br />AD on the mobile&nbsp;<br /></strong>The mobile version of the ministry's&nbsp;web:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.regjeringen.no/mobil/ad">www.regjeringen.no/mobil/ad</a>.<strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;<br />AD </strong><strong>on Twitter<br /></strong>Follow us on <a href="http://www.twitter.com/Arbeidsdep">www.twitter.com/Arbeidsdep</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;<br /><strong>Photographies</strong><br />Photographies of the political staff&nbsp;can be downloaded from&nbsp;the&nbsp;<a href="/en/dep/aid/press-centre/picture-archive.html?id=194">picture archive</a>, and from&nbsp;the Ministy's photostream at <a href="http://www.flickr.com/arbeidsdepartementet">flickr.com/arbeidsdepartementet</a>.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Find the way</strong><br />The Division also helps to locate the correct department or case officer for background material and information.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>      
